Task and Responsibilities 工作职责： 
1. To support project managers on all project activities;
协助项目经理参与项目工作；

2. To work within the engineering team and be involved in all aspects of EPC projects from design, procurement, construction, commissioning and start-up;
在工程团队内工作，参与总承包项目，设计，采购，施工，调试，到开车的各项工作;

3. Assist in the design of various plant components, equipment, systems, area, etc. and be responsible for preparation of engineering design documentation, submittal and procurement packages;
协助设计各种元件，设备，系统等，负责准备工程设计资料，提交和采购包。

4. Take part in project planning and scheduling, cost control and project commercial aspects;
参与项目计划和安排，成本控制，项目商业的方面；

Education: degree or higher in Chemical/Mechanical Engineering or equivalent related discipline
教育：本科及以上学历，机械工程、化学工程与工程学相关专业

Working Experience: Minimum 1 year relevant working experience in a project environment in the environmental technology,  chemical, pharmaceutical or energy related industries
工作经验：至少1年以上在环保，化工，制药或能源相关行业项目方面的工作经验

Technical & Professional Knowledge: 
技术和专业知识： 
1. Proven effective communication and coordination skills and team work; 
有效沟通，团队协作；
2. Learn, understand and use technical/engineering document and drawings;
学习，理解和应用技术/工程文件和图纸；
3. Good written and spoken English;
良好的英语说写能力；
